---
title: French Onion Meatloaves with Mashed Potatoes and Thyme-Roasted Carrots
description: Caramelized onions taste good on lots of things—maybe you’ve had them on burgers, sandwiches, or steaks. You probably haven’t had them on meatloaf before but trust us—there. they’re still plenty tasty. In this recipe, mini beef loaves are topped with the sweet slivers as well as a heap of melty cheese in a riff on the flavors of French onion soup. On the side, you’ve got mashed potatoes and herby roasted carrots to keep things extra warm and hearty.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/french-onion-meatloaves-9801c86d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/french-onion-meatloaves-5b9be76fae08b536324bfa42-f0938be5.pdf
